headline: TD Cowen Confident in Workday’s (WDAY) Fiscal 2026 Revenue Outlook
summary: Workday, Inc. (NASDAQ:WDAY) ranks among the best software stocks to buy right now. Following the company’s most recent earnings report, TD Cowen confirmed its Buy rating on Workday, Inc.
